{"tid":1381370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴職工會話 connect 港鐵車長","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T23:46:08.000Z","uid":63979,"like":92,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"60474a64926ea7cb872548d869f60dd44e4083be","tid":1381370,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"致巴士從業員及全港市民公開信：<br />\n<br />\n新世界第一巴士公司職工會（下稱新巴職工會）就7月21日元朗鐵路站大批市民被毆打，對持械人士襲擊市民表示極度憤怒，對相關執法部門及鐵路公司處理手法表示失望。港鐵經常聲稱自己為世界級鐵路公司，但其對事件的處理手法令人遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n過去一星期，政府就元朗事件，多次迴避問題及未有即時作出內部調查，令全港市民感覺恐慌，亦非常憤怒。新巴職工會予以強烈的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n而對於各位不畏強權，以公開姓名參與聯署的港鐵車長，新巴職工會敬佩你們的智慧及勇氣。港鐵車長們，你們並不孤單，身為巴士從業員的我們也與你們心連心，站於同一陣線。<br />\n<br />\n為表示對政府處理元朗襲擊事件偏頗，以及聲援各位參與聯署的港鐵車長，新巴職工會響應《塞爆港島》行動呼籲。<br />\n<br />\n現呼籲全港巴士從業員明天緊守崗位，安全速度駕駛，緊密照顧傷健、老弱、幼兒及孕婦。<br />\n<br />\n現本會正研究進一步行動，請各員工及市民留意事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/579355445500005/posts/1972045749564294?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F579355445500005%2Fposts%2F1972045749564294%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=43bc694f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/579355445500005/posts/1972045749564294?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"41f0db35ffb38f9e81efaf99640c7c16213e1ba3","tid":1381370,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9787c81654c62d5d8ffc06a7bce0d74be30914","tid":1381370,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />MTR 車長唔係話罷工係FAKE NEWS咩"},{"pid":"d122aa4ea8daa60ec8d1fad3081c0623b5f14389","tid":1381370,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e1587151c3fc23fbac8c57ba14e35874f9fc43","tid":1381370,"uid":289801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"其實mtr唔好聽日罷 直接8月5啦 <br />\n一波過搞大佢 聽日不合作算啦<br />\n唔好罷住<br />\n夠大型無咁易清算到"},{"pid":"13e937bb9c099205a90df5bd1485646d9097252a","tid":1381370,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c6f725ec6a1cb24babf9ca488dc2063c282ed7","tid":1381370,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:00:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aab9f73cc939f3f5910ba642d99810cf9371080","tid":1381370,"uid":63979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:14:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"819ed316e5c9d35842e45acb72228f00518c70a7","tid":1381370,"uid":288924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7edf6c75d944fbc49a6788daf31731e33f145b0","tid":1381370,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea09048270d26392fbb0ee6356e607d2f76e3d6f","tid":1381370,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"地鐵有冇得按章工作？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674e6ada2bbf5c1edb703dd334d642d7fcdca8b2","tid":1381370,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db19741a3b1761d9cc07bff8e139ec1b22dff